WEBVTT

00:00:00.792 --> 00:00:03.358
[This talk contains graphic images]

00:00:04.849 --> 00:00:07.162
So I'm sitting across from Pedro,

00:00:07.186 --> 00:00:09.371
the coyote, the human smuggler,

00:00:09.395 --> 00:00:11.814
in his cement block apartment,

00:00:12.766 --> 00:00:14.662
in a dusty Reynosa neighborhood

00:00:14.686 --> 00:00:17.140
somewhere on the US-Mexico border.

00:00:17.546 --> 00:00:18.799
It's 3am.

00:00:19.371 --> 00:00:22.301
The day before, he had asked me
to come back to his apartment.

00:00:23.006 --> 00:00:25.746
We would talk man to man.

00:00:25.770 --> 00:00:28.489
He wanted me to be there
at night and alone.

00:00:29.062 --> 00:00:31.285
I didn't know if he was setting me up,